  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A 17 week, double-blind, randomized, parallel group, four arm design outpatient study
      comparing LAAM, buprenorphine and two dose levels of methadone for the treatment of opioid
      dependence.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
